question: Retrive all purchase details
query:
SELECT p.purchase_id, p.purchase_date, p.amount, p.registration_number,
       CONCAT(c.first_name, ' ', c.last_name) AS customer_name, c.email, c.address,
       b.manufacturer, b.model, b.price,
       d.dealer_name, d.location
FROM purchases p
INNER JOIN customers c ON p.customer_id = c.customer_id
INNER JOIN bikes b ON p.bike_id = b.bike_id
INNER JOIN dealers d ON p.dealer_id = d.dealer_id;

SELECT c.customer_id, CONCAT(c.first_name, ' ', c.last_name) AS customer_name, c.email, c.phone_number, c.address
FROM customers c
INNER JOIN purchases p ON c.customer_id = p.customer_id
INNER JOIN bikes b ON p.bike_id = b.bike_id
WHERE b.model = 'Unicorn';

SELECT c.customer_id, CONCAT(c.first_name, ' ', c.last_name) AS customer_name, c.email, c.phone_number, c.address
FROM customers c
INNER JOIN purchases p ON c.customer_id = p.customer_id
INNER JOIN bikes b ON p.bike_id = b.bike_id
WHERE b.model = 'Radeon';

SELECT c.customer_id, CONCAT(c.first_name, ' ', c.last_name) AS customer_name, c.email, c.phone_number, c.address
FROM customers c
INNER JOIN purchases p ON c.customer_id = p.customer_id
INNER JOIN bikes b ON p.bike_id = b.bike_id
WHERE b.model = 'Super Splendor';

question: Which bikes have been purchased from Trio Honda
query:
SELECT 
    CONCAT(c.first_name, ' ', c.last_name) AS customer_name,p.purchase_date,p.registration_number,b.manufacturer,b.model,p.amount
FROM purchases p
INNER JOIN dealers d ON p.dealer_id = d.dealer_id
INNER JOIN bikes b ON p.bike_id = b.bike_id
INNER JOIN customers c ON p.customer_id = c.customer_id
WHERE d.dealer_name = 'Trio Honda';

SELECT c.customer_id,CONCAT (c.first_name, '', c.last_name) AS customer_name, b.bike_id, 
       b.manufacturer, b.model,p.purchase_id,p.purchase_date, p.registration_number,p.amount,d.dealer_name
FROM purchases p
INNER JOIN bikes b ON p.bike_id = b.bike_id
INNER JOIN customers c ON p.customer_id = c.customer_id
INNER JOIN dealers d ON p.dealer_id = d.dealer_id
WHERE c.first_name = 'Bob' AND c.last_name = 'Smith';

SELECT c.customer_id, CONCAT(c.first_name, '', c.last_name) AS customer_name, b.bike_id, 
       b.manufacturer, b.model, p.registration_number
FROM purchases p
INNER JOIN bikes b ON p.bike_id = b.bike_id
INNER JOIN customers c ON p.customer_id = c.customer_id
INNER JOIN dealers d ON p.dealer_id = d.dealer_id
WHERE c.customer_id='3';

question: Show me the latest purchases
query:
SELECT p.purchase_id, 
       CONCAT(c.first_name, ' ', c.last_name) AS customer_name, 
       b.model, 
       p.purchase_date,
       d.dealer_name
FROM purchases p
INNER JOIN customers c ON p.customer_id = c.customer_id
INNER JOIN bikes b ON p.bike_id = b.bike_id
INNER JOIN dealers d ON p.dealer_id = d.dealer_id
ORDER BY p.purchase_date DESC;

SELECT p.purchase_id, p.purchase_date, p.amount, p.registration_number,
       CONCAT(c.first_name, ' ', c.last_name) AS customer_name, c.email, c.address
FROM purchases p
INNER JOIN customers c ON p.customer_id = c.customer_id;

question: Retrieve the total amount spent by each customer
query:
SELECT CONCAT(c.first_name, ' ', c.last_name) AS customer_name, SUM(p.amount) AS total_spent
FROM customers c
INNER JOIN purchases p ON c.customer_id = p.customer_id
GROUP BY c.customer_id, c.first_name, c.last_name;

       b.manufacturer, b.model,b.price,p.amount
FROM purchases p

WHERE p.purchase_id ='4';

FROM customers c
JOIN purchases p ON c.customer_id = p.customer_id
JOIN bikes b ON p.bike_id = b.bike_id
GROUP BY customer_name;

SELECT CONCAT(c.first_name, ' ', c.last_name) AS customer_name, SUM(p.amount) AS total_amount_spent, count(b.bike_id) AS bikes_owned
FROM customers c
JOIN purchases p ON c.customer_id = p.customer_id
JOIN bikes b ON p.bike_id = b.bike_id
WHERE c.first_name = 'Arjun' and c.last_name = 'Nair'
GROUP BY customer_name;

JOIN purchases p ON c.customer_id = p.customer_id
JOIN bikes b ON p.bike_id = b.bike_id
WHERE c.first_name = 'Akshay' and c.last_name = 'Khare'
GROUP BY customer_name;
